iptables-builder README
===============

Simple wrapper script that helps generate iptables configuration

Copyright Â© 2012 Greg Swift
Written by: Greg Swift <greg.swift@nytefyre.net>
License: General Public License (GPL) v3

Description
===============

To help ease configuration management of iptables this script will read
ordered files from a directory and compile the system's iptables configuration
from them.

Usage
===============

* To build /etc/sysconfig/iptables from enabled rules:
     # iptables-builder

How to report bugs
===============
Visit http://github.com/gregswift/iptables-builder/issues

